Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:31.58,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}与你并肩漫步的今日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:35.25,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}便成了一生难忘的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.92,0:22:38.38,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}你不经意间的温柔
